    "result": {"data":{"markdownRemark":{"excerpt":"Hello Friends üëã, Welcome To aGuidehub! ‚ù§Ô∏è To get rid of glare in photopea, select the  and click on the glare many times. It will get rid of glare.  Today, I‚Ä¶","html":"<p>Hello Friends üëã,</p>\n<p>Welcome To aGuidehub! ‚ù§Ô∏è</p>\n<p>To get rid of glare in photopea, select the <code class=\"language-text\">clone tool</code> and click on the glare many times. It will get rid of glare. </p>\n<p>Today, I am going to show you how I get rid of glare in photopea.</p>\n<p>Table of contents</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Insert image.</li>\n<li>Create the new layer.</li>\n<li>Select the clone tool.</li>\n<li>Select the magic wand.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Let‚Äôs start with the first step.</p>\n<h3>Step 1: Insert image.</h3>\n<p>Open the photopea and Select photo, it will open a <strong><em>file</em></strong> browser or download folder you can select the image. And click the <strong><em>open</em></strong> button.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 630px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/8f13e9efa5d22a3b723a5903842b4770/e4b8a/image.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 58.22784810126582%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Photopea, image\"\n        title=\"Photopea, image\"\n        src=\"/static/8f13e9efa5d22a3b723a5903842b4770/828fb/image.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/8f13e9efa5d22a3b723a5903842b4770/ff44c/image.jpg 158w,\n/static/8f13e9efa5d22a3b723a5903842b4770/a6688/image.jpg 315w,\n/static/8f13e9efa5d22a3b723a5903842b4770/828fb/image.jpg 630w,\n/static/8f13e9efa5d22a3b723a5903842b4770/0ede0/image.jpg 945w,\n/static/8f13e9efa5d22a3b723a5903842b4770/e4b8a/image.jpg 1207w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 630px) 100vw, 630px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<h3>Step 2: Create the new layer.</h3>\n<p>Normally, Photopea would just go ahead and add the new blank layer. But by holding down the Alt / Option key while clicking the <strong><em>New Layer icon</em></strong>. If we look again in our Layers panel, we see that we now have a new blank layer named <strong><em>rid Wrinkles</em></strong>. </p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 630px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/6d3c7f105130c161221546b92167f7ee/902ab/ctrl%2Bj.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 58.22784810126582%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Photopea, ctrl+j\"\n        title=\"Photopea, ctrl+j\"\n        src=\"/static/6d3c7f105130c161221546b92167f7ee/828fb/ctrl%2Bj.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/6d3c7f105130c161221546b92167f7ee/ff44c/ctrl%2Bj.jpg 158w,\n/static/6d3c7f105130c161221546b92167f7ee/a6688/ctrl%2Bj.jpg 315w,\n/static/6d3c7f105130c161221546b92167f7ee/828fb/ctrl%2Bj.jpg 630w,\n/static/6d3c7f105130c161221546b92167f7ee/0ede0/ctrl%2Bj.jpg 945w,\n/static/6d3c7f105130c161221546b92167f7ee/902ab/ctrl%2Bj.jpg 1204w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 630px) 100vw, 630px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<h3>Step 3: Select the clone tool.</h3>\n<p>Select the <strong><em>clone tool</em></strong> from the toolbar on the left side of your workspace.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 630px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/a712cbfb792b2be01f6c9bd112441d39/902ab/clone-tool.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 57.59493670886076%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Photopea, clone-tool\"\n        title=\"Photopea, clone-tool\"\n        src=\"/static/a712cbfb792b2be01f6c9bd112441d39/828fb/clone-tool.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/a712cbfb792b2be01f6c9bd112441d39/ff44c/clone-tool.jpg 158w,\n/static/a712cbfb792b2be01f6c9bd112441d39/a6688/clone-tool.jpg 315w,\n/static/a712cbfb792b2be01f6c9bd112441d39/828fb/clone-tool.jpg 630w,\n/static/a712cbfb792b2be01f6c9bd112441d39/0ede0/clone-tool.jpg 945w,\n/static/a712cbfb792b2be01f6c9bd112441d39/902ab/clone-tool.jpg 1204w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 630px) 100vw, 630px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>Press <strong><em>Alt + Left</em></strong> mouse key. Left mouse over the area you want to clone. Notice my picture. The area I want to clone will show a <strong><em>plus sign (+)</em></strong>.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 630px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/36d24d55ffcb2e11c184bcd3a46274f9/deb44/press-alt.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 56.32911392405063%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Photopea, press-alt\"\n        title=\"Photopea, press-alt\"\n        src=\"/static/36d24d55ffcb2e11c184bcd3a46274f9/828fb/press-alt.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/36d24d55ffcb2e11c184bcd3a46274f9/ff44c/press-alt.jpg 158w,\n/static/36d24d55ffcb2e11c184bcd3a46274f9/a6688/press-alt.jpg 315w,\n/static/36d24d55ffcb2e11c184bcd3a46274f9/828fb/press-alt.jpg 630w,\n/static/36d24d55ffcb2e11c184bcd3a46274f9/0ede0/press-alt.jpg 945w,\n/static/36d24d55ffcb2e11c184bcd3a46274f9/deb44/press-alt.jpg 1212w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 630px) 100vw, 630px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>Using the Clone Tool in Photospea Online. Please right-click the mouse. After some time a parameter table will appear. I‚Äôll set the size to 15% then ok.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 630px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/3374338c01ec264a50804771a192d062/c0266/clone-size.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 57.59493670886076%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Photopea, clone-size\"\n        title=\"Photopea, clone-size\"\n        src=\"/static/3374338c01ec264a50804771a192d062/828fb/clone-size.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/3374338c01ec264a50804771a192d062/ff44c/clone-size.jpg 158w,\n/static/3374338c01ec264a50804771a192d062/a6688/clone-size.jpg 315w,\n/static/3374338c01ec264a50804771a192d062/828fb/clone-size.jpg 630w,\n/static/3374338c01ec264a50804771a192d062/0ede0/clone-size.jpg 945w,\n/static/3374338c01ec264a50804771a192d062/c0266/clone-size.jpg 1205w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 630px) 100vw, 630px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>Then, release the Atl key! and then <strong><em>left-click</em></strong> on the area you want to delete (reflective area). Just like that until your photo is perfect.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 630px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/a3e92aa36ac5ae0c5076447f2d98bc17/09fd1/click-on-page.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 57.59493670886076%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Photopea, click-on-page\"\n        title=\"Photopea, click-on-page\"\n        src=\"/static/a3e92aa36ac5ae0c5076447f2d98bc17/828fb/click-on-page.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/a3e92aa36ac5ae0c5076447f2d98bc17/ff44c/click-on-page.jpg 158w,\n/static/a3e92aa36ac5ae0c5076447f2d98bc17/a6688/click-on-page.jpg 315w,\n/static/a3e92aa36ac5ae0c5076447f2d98bc17/828fb/click-on-page.jpg 630w,\n/static/a3e92aa36ac5ae0c5076447f2d98bc17/0ede0/click-on-page.jpg 945w,\n/static/a3e92aa36ac5ae0c5076447f2d98bc17/09fd1/click-on-page.jpg 1208w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 630px) 100vw, 630px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<h3>Step 4: Select the magic wand.</h3>\n<p>Select the <strong><em>magic-wand</em></strong> from the toolbar on the left side of your workspace.\nSeparate the left and right eye with the Magic Wand tool in photoshop online to separate objects.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 630px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/d1d3762a6d3be27e9749541662ed68bc/5af5e/magic-wand.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 58.22784810126582%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Photopea, magic-wand\"\n        title=\"Photopea, magic-wand\"\n        src=\"/static/d1d3762a6d3be27e9749541662ed68bc/828fb/magic-wand.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/d1d3762a6d3be27e9749541662ed68bc/ff44c/magic-wand.jpg 158w,\n/static/d1d3762a6d3be27e9749541662ed68bc/a6688/magic-wand.jpg 315w,\n/static/d1d3762a6d3be27e9749541662ed68bc/828fb/magic-wand.jpg 630w,\n/static/d1d3762a6d3be27e9749541662ed68bc/0ede0/magic-wand.jpg 945w,\n/static/d1d3762a6d3be27e9749541662ed68bc/5af5e/magic-wand.jpg 1203w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 630px) 100vw, 630px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>Normally, Photopea would just go ahead and add the new blank layer. But by holding down the Alt / Option key while clicking the <strong><em>New Layer icon</em></strong>. If we look again at our Layers panel.</p>\n<p>Final result.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 630px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/16859a230a009a225c2311724052a0fe/5af5e/layer-2.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 57.59493670886076%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Photopea, layer-2\"\n        title=\"Photopea, layer-2\"\n        src=\"/static/16859a230a009a225c2311724052a0fe/828fb/layer-2.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/16859a230a009a225c2311724052a0fe/ff44c/layer-2.jpg 158w,\n/static/16859a230a009a225c2311724052a0fe/a6688/layer-2.jpg 315w,\n/static/16859a230a009a225c2311724052a0fe/828fb/layer-2.jpg 630w,\n/static/16859a230a009a225c2311724052a0fe/0ede0/layer-2.jpg 945w,\n/static/16859a230a009a225c2311724052a0fe/5af5e/layer-2.jpg 1203w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 630px) 100vw, 630px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>When you follow the above steps then it will get rid of glare in photopea.</p>\n<p>All the best üëç</p>","frontmatter":{"title":"How to get rid of glare in photopea?","tags":["Photopea"],"date":"October 26, 2022","description":"Adding to get rid of glare in photopea example with step-by-step guide - aGuidehub.","social_image":"media/template/photopea.jpg"}},"prev":{"frontmatter":{"title":"How to get length of a map in golang?"},"fields":{"slug":"/blog/2022-10-26-golang-get-length-of-map/"}},"next":{"frontmatter":{"title":"How to get rid of wrinkles on photopea?"},"fields":{"slug":"/blog/2022-10-25-how-to-get-rid-of-wrinkles-on-photopea/"}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/blog/2022-10-26-how-to-get-rid-of-a-glare-in-photopea/","prevSlug":"/blog/2022-10-26-golang-get-length-of-map/","nextSlug":"/blog/2022-10-25-how-to-get-rid-of-wrinkles-on-photopea/"}},
